<section class="about-section">
  <h1 class="about-title">About Us</h1>
  <p class="about-introduction">
    Welcome to SwachhSankalp. Our mission is to promote cleanliness and
    sustainability. We are a passionate community dedicated to creating a
    cleaner, greener future.
  </p>
  <div class="about-content">
    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>
      SwachhSankalp started as a small group of environmentally conscious
      individuals who wanted to make a difference. Over time, we have grown into
      a large community with members from all walks of life, united by a common
      goal: to promote and practice sustainable living.
    </p>
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      Our mission is to inspire and empower individuals and communities to take
      action towards a cleaner environment. Through various initiatives, we aim
      to reduce waste, promote recycling, and encourage sustainable practices.
    </p>
    <h2>Why Cleanliness Matters</h2>
    <p>
      Cleanliness is more than just an aesthetic value; it’s a crucial aspect of
      health and environmental sustainability. A clean environment:
    </p>
    <ul class="awareness-list">
      <li>Prevents diseases by reducing the spread of germs and pathogens.</li>
      <li>
        Promotes mental well-being by creating pleasant and healthy
        surroundings.
      </li>
      <li>Protects wildlife and natural habitats from pollution and waste.</li>
      <li>Enhances the beauty and value of our communities.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Our Awareness Initiatives</h2>
    <p>
      Raising awareness about cleanliness is at the core of our mission. Here’s
      how we do it:
    </p>
    <ul class="awareness-list">
      <li>
        <strong>Community Clean-Up Drives:</strong> Organizing regular clean-up
        events to remove litter and beautify public spaces.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Educational Workshops:</strong> Conducting workshops to educate
        people about the importance of cleanliness and sustainable living.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Public Campaigns:</strong> Launching campaigns to promote
        cleanliness and encourage responsible waste disposal.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>School Programs:</strong> Engaging with schools to teach
        children the value of maintaining a clean environment.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Our Impact</h2>
    <p>
      SwachhSankalp has made significant strides in promoting cleanliness and
      sustainability. Here are some of our achievements:
    </p>
    <ul class="impact-list">
      <li>
        <strong>Waste Reduction:</strong> Our clean-up drives have successfully
        removed tons of waste from streets, beaches, and parks.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Community Engagement:</strong> Thousands of volunteers have
        participated in our events, spreading the message of cleanliness far and
        wide.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Sustainable Practices:</strong> Many communities have adopted
        sustainable practices such as composting, recycling, and reducing
        plastic use due to our initiatives.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Join Us</h2>
    <p>
      Be part of our journey. Whether you want to volunteer at an event,
      contribute to our blog, or simply learn more about sustainability, there
      is a place for you at SwachhSankalp. Together, we can make a difference.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

